{"tid":2095821,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV 晚吹 - 有酒今晚飲","createTime":"2020-07-05T18:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T16:21:04.000Z","uid":14600,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35e828b64fad1398a9326d49781cbd708fed3871","tid":2095821,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:21:55.000Z","msg":"節目簡介：<br />\n<br />\n古今中外，人類的品酒文化源遠流長！結婚時、畢業時、離別時，人們都愛以酒相伴&hellip;人生中的悲歡離合、喜怒哀樂，每一事每一物都總能以美酒作搭配。若說「美酒」能說「故事」，大概亦不假！全新一輯《晚吹》系列作品：《晚吹：有酒今晩吹》，主持人會以「一枝酒，一個故事」出發，與每集受邀請的明星嘉賓，一齊「堅飲、堅醉、堅吹水」。未醉之前，大家固然能侃侃而談，有紋有路；醉了之後，彼此更會放下隔膜，爆料講真話！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/talker-chit-chat-drink/talker--chit-chat-drinke8craft-gin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Ftalker-chit-chat-drink%2Ftalker--chit-chat-drinke8craft-gin&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj34leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=cc196622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/talker-chit-chat-drink/talker--chit-chat-drinke8craft-gin</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次睇呢個晚吹新系列, 睇咗金剛嗰集, 發覺幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金剛講戴綠帽嗰到真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df21c2c46080411657b9864980e4b629919b604d","tid":2095821,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"魚哥嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa9bbe86842e319a35944fa472c8a855b92cc33","tid":2095821,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"娟娟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf7151e9dd0f95fd6503bad4c99587097673acd","tid":2095821,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:33:17.000Z","msg"